Smuggler
Smugglers move goods, people, and information across borders that would
otherwise stop them cold. In the Rifts world of faction checkpoints, travel
restrictions, and black markets, a skilled Smuggler is one of the most
economically valuable people alive.

Smugglers choose from Rogue, Pilot, Technical, and Espionage skill categories.
They are experts in concealment, bribery, route planning, and fast talking
at checkpoints. Many maintain contacts across multiple factions.

Attribute requirements: IQ 10, MA 11.
Starting equipment: Civilian vehicle (represented in-game as travel access),
concealed compartment kit, personal radio, one concealed sidearm, forged
shipping documents, and a working contact list.
